 - Created by sahgarg on 1/12/2018.
Modification Log:
Prachi Nandgaonkar      Jan 24, 2018         [PC-2565] Updated helper.PC_Graph to show document's record type instead of
											 generic word 'Document'
Shabda Bhujad           Jan 26, 2018         [PC-2682] Updated slds styles so that the field set display matches the specs
Vijay Kashikar          Feb 09, 2018         [PC-2771] Made changes so as to listen to force:refreshView
Sahil Garg              Feb 12, 2018         [PC-2776] Added accordion style to expand and collapse
Prachi Nandgaonkar      Feb 13, 2018         [PC-2794] Removed padding to align with Document Action Ribbon
Satheesh Kumar          Jul 23, 2020         [PC-6483] Added PC_Document_Name__c field in header section
Haritha Reddy           Jan 15, 2021         [PC-7204] Updated SLDS of Document name and Status from Truncate to Wrap
Haritha Reddy           Feb 11, 2021         [PC-7409] Updated logic to clear document details field set values before reloading the data
Haritha Reddy           Feb 17, 2021         [PC-7425] Added CSS to wrap words in Document name and Status
